  "title": "Vegan Mac & Cheese",
  "subtitle": null,
  "excerpt": "Vegan Mac & Cheese. A home-cook's recipe from Rebecca's collection, kept in the family rotation.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "From Rebecca's personal cookbook, a recipe she's made many times in her own kitchen.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Vegan Mac & Cheese. A British home-cook's dish, the kind of recipe families adjust across generations. Adjustable for what you need.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A weeknight-friendly recipe: most of the work is the prep, and the cooking takes care of itself.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
